{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game is still in early development so will undergo many changes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What is Rising Army?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A strategy camp sim game where you manage and command your army, training each individual troop and upgrading your camp. Satisfy your King by completing missions and epic battles against enemies. Lead your Lord to legend!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2999050/extras/buildgif.gif?t=1733996602\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Manage your army</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Manage resources and keep your army's morale high by carefully planning your strategies between missions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Promote captains and assign special roles in your camp improving your commander skills.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Don't disappoint the King and carry out his will by completing the tasks assigned to you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2999050/extras/traingif.gif?t=1733996602\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Train your troops</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Each member of the army will have unique characteristics, traits, and specific needs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> You can train and equip each individual troop, striving for the right balance in your army.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Don't get too attached to them; in every battle, death will be permanent!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2999050/extras/mapgif.gif?t=1733996602\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore the maps</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Explore the various regions of the kingdom where the King will require your services.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Noticing points of interest might lead you to rewards or unexpected encounters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Search and loot everything that could be useful for your army.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2999050/extras/battlegif.gif?t=1733996602\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Lead your army on the battlefied</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Fight in epic battles with various objectives.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Each victory will increase the King's satisfaction.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Lead your army to glory by gaining experience.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2999050/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733996602","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2999050/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1733996602","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2999050/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733996602","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2999050/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733996602","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game is still in early development so will undergo many changes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What is Rising Army?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A strategy camp